455
00:27:26,444 --> 00:27:29,984
Tentu saja. Ibu tiriku sudah mengamuk karenanya.

456
00:27:30,284 --> 00:27:31,544
Woo Jae.

457
00:27:32,114 --> 00:27:35,184
Aku punya keinginan baru. Dan itu adalah...

458
00:27:35,254 --> 00:27:38,384
