Bukankah seharusnya kita pergi membantu mereka?

481
00:29:21,394 --> 00:29:22,924
Tidak, biarkan mereka menikmati momen mereka.

482
00:29:24,824 --> 00:29:25,824
Mari kita istirahat sejenak.

483
00:29:28,564 --> 00:29:29,564
Wah, dingin sekali.

484
00:29:29,834 --> 00:29:31,604
Aku lelah, tapi tetap saja...

485
