568
00:35:37,904 --> 00:35:38,904
Aku Lemon!

569
00:35:39,234 --> 00:35:40,234
Semangka, dua!

570
00:35:40,504 --> 00:35:41,574
Semangka, semangka!

571
00:35:41,934 --> 00:35:43,974
