573
00:35:48,114 --> 00:35:50,314
Aku bahagia.

574
00:35:52,214 --> 00:35:54,614
Sutradara, Anda memiliki energi yang luar biasa...

575
00:35:55,384 --> 00:35:56,984
Suasananya sangat cerah dan positif.

576
00:35:57,424 --> 00:36:02,224
