581
00:36:19,544 --> 00:36:20,714
Sejujurnya, sudah lama sekali...

582
00:36:22,074 --> 00:36:23,514
Dulu aku benar-benar cengeng.

583
00:36:24,714 --> 00:36:25,714
Benar-benar?

584
00:36:27,354 --> 00:36:29,854
Ayolah, aku sulit mempercayai itu.

585
00:36:30,584 --> 00:36:32,284
Tidak, saya serius.

586
00:36:33,654 --> 00:36:35,454
Saat itu, aku sangat sengsara,

587
